{"id": 2084, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪种道歉经不起推敲？", "description": "“你说我错了那我就错了呗，你还有什么不满意？”（题图来自：Giphy）", "record_count": 1975, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171222114109QtzBKox75U9LXWSm.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-28T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 257024, "content": "日本式韩国式道歉最假", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163079}, {"id": 257280, "content": "眼神不敢直视你的道歉。emmmmmm是吧", "image": "img/option/option/20171229225948zbYeult7JNiUnXIp", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219375}, {"id": 257281, "content": "对不起 ，你是个好人，但是我不爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1192475}, {"id": 257026, "content": "道歉就意味着自己犯了错，犯了错就不值得原谅。说了对不起，依旧无法真正得到原谅！", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1091141}, {"id": 257027, "content": "怪我咯！", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1171765}, {"id": 257028, "content": "我不是都说了对不起了嘛，看你的表情", "image": null, "praise_count": 14, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 57280}, {"id": 258308, "content": "隨你便吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1231205}, {"id": 257029, "content": "这不是我的本意…", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224423}, {"id": 257030, "content": "哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1144109}, {"id": 257031, "content": "诶哟~对不起嘛…\n(｡･ˇ_ˇ･｡:)", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1219249}, {"id": 257032, "content": "好啦 别生气我错了 但是你也有不对的地方……巴拉巴拉 你妹这种顺带指责的干脆一边凉快去", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1108861}, {"id": 257033, "content": "对不起，我的锅", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1191880}, {"id": 257034, "content": "对不起行了吧/我错了行了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1107059}, {"id": 257035, "content": "我不是已经说对不起了吗。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224465}, {"id": 257036, "content": "A：你不知道你错了之后需要道歉吗？\nB：好吧，那我给你道歉。\n\n然后就没有然后了", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224471}, {"id": 257037, "content": "sorry啊。。。我也很委屈的。。（她真是这么给我说的，到现在没理她）", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224479}, {"id": 257038, "content": "我说对不起还不行吗？（手动再见）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 939196}, {"id": 257040, "content": "对着我释放完情绪，然后“诚意”的道歉。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224508}, {"id": 257041, "content": "好好好，那就对不起嘛", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 501680}, {"id": 257042, "content": "不好意西哈，你看我怎么能这样那样的。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213244}, {"id": 257043, "content": "嗯，是我错了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224517}, {"id": 257044, "content": "对不起，行吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 855687}, {"id": 257046, "content": "对不起，我爱你", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1198027}, {"id": 257047, "content": "想全部都点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141963}, {"id": 257048, "content": "临签合同反水，仗着没签随便道歉", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165907}, {"id": 257050, "content": "分手后的“对不起”。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719706}, {"id": 257051, "content": "对不起好吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098071}, {"id": 257563, "content": "哈哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227752}, {"id": 257052, "content": "反正你对我来说也不重要原不原谅随便好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224566}, {"id": 257053, "content": "都是我的問題，你沒問題", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1088451}, {"id": 257054, "content": "是是是，您是对的，我错了，行吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110798}, {"id": 257055, "content": "我都道歉了你还要怎么样", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1104625}, {"id": 257057, "content": "对不起了，这都是因为…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790711}, {"id": 257571, "content": "我就是这样的，你又不是不知道~\n对不起咯", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227803}, {"id": 257827, "content": "我的错，行了吧，不管怎样都是我的错。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1228845}, {"id": 257061, "content": "立马解释原因，还提出解决方案，但不见得到时候真会这么做。只想告诉他一句，早干嘛去了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 952886}, {"id": 255782, "content": "自恋式道歉，说抱歉只是因为自己受到影响，而不是真的体会到对方的感受", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 257062, "content": "“旅客朋友们，很抱歉的通知您，……（航班延误/取消），对此我们深表歉意。”", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 902112}, {"id": 257574, "content": "最火的是，明明是她莫名其妙和自己闹变扭，反过来和你道歉的时候还总在那哭，哭就算了，还边说“对不起”顺带还说一些引起别人误会的话，让别人误以为是我怎么怎么滴了，顿时火气就上来了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1227803}, {"id": 255783, "content": "推卸责任式道歉，“我错也错得无关紧要，核心的问题不清楚不知道不关我事”", "image": null, "praise_count": 62, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 257063, "content": "道歉就道歉，有什么了不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1140029}, {"id": 255784, "content": "你还想要我怎样式道歉，只是想尽快摆脱舆论谴责而不是真心悔过", "image": null, "praise_count": 337, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 257064, "content": "对不起，", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833873}, {"id": 259368, "content": "你说的都对", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1238300}, {"id": 257065, "content": "不知悔改的对不起", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 742448}, {"id": 257066, "content": "谁错能怎滴，非说我错那就错吧，你赢了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224604}, {"id": 257067, "content": "我的错好了吧？我都说对不起了，你还想干嘛？有病啊你(这句话简直能把人气死)", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221392}, {"id": 257069, "content": "我错了，行了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1224617}, {"id": 288814, "content": "行行行，我的错好吧……最反感好吧这个词，显得无所谓，敷衍性极强", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1380759}, {"id": 257070, "content": "我错了我错了，反正你永远都是对的", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 5509}]}